name: Ski Tip Wine Bottle Holder
description:
Single wine bottle holder made from the tip of old skis.  

Perfect for the wine (or beer) lover who also loves skiing.  Or is it the skier who also loves wine?  

Works best with 750ml wine bottles (i.e. standard wine bottle) and many beer bombers too.

Image here is only a sample. To see more, please visit:
http://ascensionwoodcraft.com/what-we-make/

We will confirm which one you want after your order is received. Requests welcomed.
